query:
query getHandlesQuery($categoryId: Int!, $subCategoryId: Int, $internal: Boolean, $orderProfileType: OrderProfileType!) {
  getHandles(categoryId: $categoryId, subCategoryId: $subCategoryId, internal: $internal, orderProfileType: $orderProfileType) {
    name
    spacecraftHandleId
    finish
    budgetType
    height
    imageUrl
    pitch
    isEnabled
    handleType
    shutterFamilyIds
    __typename
  }
}
